name: Honey Stinger Peanut Butter Dark Chocolate Protein Cracker Bar
categories: Peanut Butter Dark Chocolate Protein Cracker
description:
Now packed with 10 grams of plant-based protein! Creamy organic peanut butter and honey sandwiched in hearty multigrain crackers and covered in a smooth dark chocolate for a hit of energy that isn’t just another bar. As a bonus the chocolate coating helps prevent cracker breakage and excessive crumbs, functional chocolate, what a concept!Ingredients: organic dark chocolate (organic cane sugar, organic chocolate liquor, organic cocoa butter, organic soy lecithin added as an emulsifier and organic vanilla), organic multi-grain cracker with sea salt (organic wheat flour, organic canola oil, organic cracked wheat, organic spelt, organic rye, organic barley, organic triticale, organic oats, organic flax, organic sesame seeds, organic sugar, sea salt and organic yeast), organic peanut butter (organic peanuts and organic palm oil, salt), organic pea protein, organic honey.Allergens – contains: soy, wheat and peanuts.Made in a facility that processes: peanuts, egg, coconut, milk and other tree nuts.
